===Noun===
'''eudemonia''' alternately '''eudaimonia''', '''eudaemonia'''
# The greatest good for an individual human being: an activity characterized by objective flourishing across a lifetime, and brought about through the exercise of moral virtue, practical wisdom, and rationality
# Roughly (and poorly) translated as "happiness"

